":387883,"uid":44641,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T04:23:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>相見是意外　見不到才是應該</blockquote><br />\n入黎就係想講喱句<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁講過第二句<br />\n<br />\n我沒有在雪上期待炭 多高興<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"828872d4a89171c185569ce8f6765326141e12ad","tid":387883,"uid":135416,"like":3,"dislike":9,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T04:23:40.000Z","msg":"最動人時光未必地老天荒<br />\n難忘的因你太念念才難忘<br />\n容易抱住誰10年  最難是放<br />\n<br />\n難道沒練習太耐  感覺都追不回來<br />\n我有時仍很怕路過你從前的家<br />\n往事若然未落幕  再揭起有害嗎<br />\n<br />\n其實你是一幅畫 狠狠往這舊人心上掛"},{"pid":"0b2de3d4cf400286eba852a6fd7202e14c3dc9fb","tid":387883,"uid":105243,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T04:24:33.000Z","msg":"你最近還好嗎"},{"pid":"18ecbf5909718e0b38c833f2cc0b95a5b8d96515","tid":387883,"uid":23039,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T04:26:18.000Z","msg":"你說你怕太濕　我說我怕太親密<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"382a47db21d0a1ca3371dc9399cdc6ff5e63e9c4","tid":387883,"uid":59353,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T04:26:18.000Z","msg":"神遇到　佛碰到　但我希望碰到我"},{"pid":"dae90910bd8ef7a6e0229ce6557162c2be41c538","tid":387883,"uid":143645,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T04:28:54.000Z","msg":"耿耿於懷從前的愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea48a1c02c1916bab778727abe3ba412c2f3dab1","tid":387883,"uid":87357,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T04:30:06.000Z","msg":"當一個人和一個人既愛又無奈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24553f72f23f37dfe8636811d8b34207bac9fba1","tid":387883,"uid":21001,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T04:30:35.000Z","msg":"然後總推說你是人 你是凡人<br />\n犧牲我乃是求生本能"},{"pid":"4c6cac9317bae0b21a07e9a6df0ff7c48b8e9454","tid